---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-32 flex flex-col items-start gap-6">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400 text-xs font-medium">
    <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
      <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-indigo-400 opacity-75"></span>
      <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-indigo-500"></span>
    </span>
        Disponível para novos desafios
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
        David <br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-cyan-400">
      Full Stack Developer & SRE
    </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
        Desenvolvedor Full Stack especializado em <span class="text-slate-200">.NET</span> e <span class="text-slate-200">Vue.js</span>.
        Com sólida experiência em infraestrutura, foco em criar sistemas escaláveis, seguros e automatizados.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4">
        <a
                href="#projetos"
                class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white font-semibold transition-all shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20"
        >
            Ver Projetos
        </a>
        <a
                href="https://linkedin.com/in/seu-perfil"
                target="_blank"
                class="px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-slate-200 border border-slate-700 font-semibold transition-all"
        >
            LinkedIn
        </a>
    </div>
</section>